      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 was used with documented release notes and regression test suite. Version control records confirm the solver build used for all production runs. SQA level 2 is satisfied."
    },
    {
