      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests or benchmark comparisons must confirm solver implementation is free of coding errors at the level required for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmark cases were executed and compared against published DNS data. Observed second-order spatial convergence confirmed. Code verification requirement at level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
