      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for the primary QoI (hemolysis index) and must indicate discretization error below 5% at the operating points of interest.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted at 5 L/min, 3000 RPM operating point. GCI for normalised hemolysis index was 3.1%, satisfying the 5% threshold. Medium mesh (4.2 M cells) selected for production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
