      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) must agree with experimental measurements within the combined experimental and numerical uncertainty band at all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "RH predictions at all five flow-speed combinations fall within ±15% of experimental values, which is within the combined uncertainty band. The acceptance criterion RH < 1 relative to predicate is satisfied at all points."
